External Login
===============

The *External Login* project is the continuation of the [Authentication Manager project](http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/auth_manager/), originally developed for Joomla! 1.5, and now compatible with Joomla! @JOOMLAVERSION@.x. Documentation can be found in the [wiki pages](https://github.com/chdemko/joomla-external-login/wiki).

Build
-----

Simply execute `composer install` and `ant` on the command line and get the built packages in the `build` directory.

~~~bash
$ composer install
$ ant
~~~

